title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Dec 27 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Dec 27 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2:

EIB Guest Host Michael Berry, from NewsRadio 740 KTRH in Houston, welcomes Nick Searcy, who was at the Capitol to talk about his latest project, the film Capitol Punishment. For a full hour, Nick discusses what he saw firsthand on January 6th, and how President Trump's enemies are seeking to twist what happened to disqualify him.  

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
